{"tid":188741,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"香港第一位職業棒球員！","createTime":"2017-04-06T02:03:46.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-06T02:06:37.000Z","uid":882,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"83ae1a5562c020fd94142fb1fa4919185a642c03","tid":188741,"uid":882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T02:03:46.000Z","msg":"香港棒球隊投手趙嗣淦於4月5出發到捷克落班，將效力球隊奧林匹亞布蘭斯科（OlympiaBlansko）在當地聯賽披甲，成為首位土生土長的香港職業棒球員。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n現年26歲的趙嗣淦擅長下鉤投球，曾於2015年初到台灣隨職業棒球隊義大犀牛參與春訓,去年也來台參加戰力外測試但是未獲得任何球隊的青睞<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aec2a1ecc66efadc89e23d27d990c3f4e693dfa7","tid":188741,"uid":62073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T02:06:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />add oil"}]}